go for the catch
Homonym Number:
Word Class: phrase
Sense Number:
Definition:[shearing] to attempt to take the last sheep in a catching pen before the bell.


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
See: catch
Pronunciation:
